1) **Install**
```
pip install --user malwi
```

2) **Run**
```
malwi examples/malicious
```

3) **Evaluate**: a [recent zero-day](https://socket.dev/blog/malicious-pypi-package-targets-discord-developers-with-RAT) detected with high confidence
```
